As a paralegal, I would prepare affidavits and other documents, such as legal correspondence, by reviewing and analyzing relevant information, drafting and editing documents, and ensuring accuracy and completeness. I would also organize and maintain documents in a paper or electronic filing system, ensuring that all documents are properly labeled, dated, and stored in a secure and accessible location. This would involve creating and maintaining a filing system, both physical and digital, and ensuring that all documents are properly indexed and cross-referenced. Additionally, I would ensure that all documents are properly signed and notarized, and that all necessary certifications and acknowledgments are obtained.
